            <b>About RedStore</b>
        </MudText>
        <MudText Align="Align.Center">
            RedStore is a Swiss-based mobile app, operating in Silk Road countries, presenting e-commerce products to millions of new buyers. By listing your products on RedStore, you can start promoting them to over 225 millions of buyers.
        </MudText>
    </div>

